p.govuk-body style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  | We hope that all is well with you and the volunteers at
  =<> @group_name
  | . We recently sent a letter to you from Sir Martyn Lewis CBE about the outcome of your nomination for the Queen’s Award for Voluntary Service. However, we are including the text of the letter in this email, in case it has not arrived with you yet.

p.govuk-body style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
